==机场交通==

[[公共汽车|公共汽车]]和[[出租车|出租车]]是机场往返[[芒市|芒市]]城区仅有的[[公共交通|公共交通工具]]，机场至芒市城区通行2路、6路<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dh.ynairport.com/traffic.jhtml|title=机场交通|last=|first=|date=|website=dh.ynairport.com|publisher=德宏芒市机场|access-date=2017-08-26|quote=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814095447/http://dh.ynairport.com/traffic.jhtml|archivedate=2017-08-14}}</ref>及机场专线公交<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=芒市公交机场专线执行票价公示 |url=http://www.dhms.gov.cn/jtj/Web/_F0_0_048M3ZMW553N7K6VO49UJW4RIK.htm |newspaper=芒市交通运输局 |location= |date=2019-01-19 |access-date=2019-09-02 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122130520/http://www.dhms.gov.cn/jtj/Web/_F0_0_048M3ZMW553N7K6VO49UJW4RIK.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[瑞丽航空|瑞丽航空]]开通了芒市机场至[[瑞丽市|瑞丽]]城区的往返大巴<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.carnoc.com/list/296/296988.html |title=瑞丽航空开通芒市机场—瑞丽免费大巴 |author=陈逍潇 |date=2014-10-19 |website=news.carnoc.com |publisher=云南信息报 |access-date=2017-08-26 |quote= |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903114833/http://news.carnoc.com/list/296/296988.html |archivedate=2017-09-03 }}</ref>，需凭瑞丽航空的相关登机牌搭乘<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cj.sina.com.cn/article/detail/5227458836/488850?column=consume&ch=9|title=对话-瑞丽航空总经理：小型航司就要快狠准|last=|first=|date=2017-11-20|website=cj.sina.com.cn|publisher=航旅圈|access-date=2017-11-21|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201043444/http://cj.sina.com.cn/article/detail/5227458836/488850?column=consume&ch=9|archivedate=2017-12-01}}</ref>。

==事故==

*2004年11月23日，[[中国国际航空|中国国际航空]][[中国西南航空|西南分公司]]CA4455航班，在执行昆明至芒市航班任务降落时冲出跑道，最后停在跑道外100多米的安全道上，机上乘客顺利下机，飞机无损伤。事故原因不明，据称飞机降落时恰逢打雷，有说法认为这是发生事故的天气原因。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.peacehall.com/news/gb/china/2004/11/200411240252.shtml|title=国航西南公司波音飞机在云南芒市机场冲出跑道|last=|first=|date=2004-11-24|website=www.peacehall.com|publisher=新华网|access-date=2017-08-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903073755/https://www.peacehall.com/news/gb/china/2004/11/200411240252.shtml|archivedate=2017-09-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.carnoc.com/list/45/45349.html|title=国航波音客机在云南芒市机场冲出跑道|last=|first=|date=2004-11-24|website=news.carnoc.com|publisher=新华网|access-date=2017-08-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903073613/http://news.carnoc.com/list/45/45349.html|archivedate=2017-09-03}}</ref>

